#. type: Title =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Install OpenRefine"
msgstr "Installer OpenRefine"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:6
msgid "Install software required for activities later in the course"
msgstr "Installer le logiciel requis pour les activités ultérieures du cours"

#. type: Positional ($1) AttributeList argument for macro 'image'
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "Open Refine Logo"
msgstr "Logo d'Open Refine"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "data-mobilization::open-refine-logo.png"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:13
msgid "https://openrefine.org/[OpenRefine^] is a tool with a set of features for working with tabular data that improves the overall quality of a dataset.  It is an application that runs on your own computer as a small web server, and in order to use it your web browser should point at that web server.  So, think of OpenRefine as a personal and private web application."
msgstr "https://openrefine.org/[OpenRefine^] est un outil contenant un ensemble de fonctionnalités pour travailler avec des données tabulaires, qui améliore la qualité globale d'un jeu de données. C'est une application qui s'exécute sur votre ordinateur comme mini serveur web. Pour l'utiliser, votre navigateur web devrait pointer vers ce serveur web. Donc, considérez OpenRefine comme une application web personnelle et privée."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:18
msgid "We will use OpenRefine during the data management portion of the course, especially during the practical exercises.  It will be necessary to install OpenRefine on your laptop.  If you are a skilled computer user, you can follow these steps to install the software on your computer.  If you are not confident, please ask for help. Refer to the https://openrefine.org/download.html[OpenRefine download page^] for more details."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:20
msgid "Administrative passwords may be required to install software."
msgstr "Des mots de passe administrateurs peuvent être requis pour installer ces logiciels."

#. type: Title ==
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "Installation Requirements"
msgstr "Conditions requises pour l’installation"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:24
msgid "Linux users only: Java JRE installed."
msgstr "Seulement pour les utilisateurs de Linux : Java JRE installé."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:25
msgid "Google Chrome, Microsoft Edge or Mozilla Firefox installed.  Internet Explorer is not supported."
msgstr "Google Chrome, Microsoft Edge ou Mozilla Firefox installés. Internet Explorer n'est pas pris en charge."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:27
msgid "The latest stable release is OpenRefine 3.4.1, released on September 24, 2020. Detailed installation instructions are available at https://docs.openrefine.org/manual/installing/[^]."
msgstr "La dernière version stable est OpenRefine 3.4.1, publiée le 24 septembre 2020. Les instructions d'installation détaillées sont disponibles sur https://docs.openrefine.org/manual/installing/[^]."

#. type: Title ==
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "Installation on MS Windows"
msgstr "Installation sur MS Windows"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:31
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:44
msgid "Download the https://github.com/OpenRefine/OpenRefine/releases/download/3.4.1/openrefine-win-with-java-3.4.1.zip[Windows kit *with embedded Java*].  Choose to save the file rather than open it."
msgstr "Téléchargez le https://github.com/OpenRefine/OpenRefine/releases/download/3.4.1/openrefine-win-with-java-3.4.1.zip[Kit Windows *with embedded Java*]. Choisissez d'enregistrer le fichier plutôt que de l'ouvrir."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:32
msgid "Find the downloaded file.  Right click it, and choose \"Extract all…\". Unzip, and double-click on openrefine.exe or refine.bat if the former does not work."
msgstr "Trouvez le fichier téléchargé. Faites un clic droit dessus et choisissez \"Extract all…\". Dézippez, et double-cliquez sur openrefine.exe ou refine.bat si le premier ne fonctionne pas."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:33
msgid "A command window will appear (don't close it) and soon after a new web browser window will show the application."
msgstr "Une fenêtre de commande apparaîtra (ne la fermez pas) et aussitôt, une nouvelle fenêtre de navigateur Web affichera l'application."

#. type: Block title
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "Detailed instructions for MS Windows (click to expand)"
msgstr "Instructions détaillées pour MS Windows (cliquez pour développer)"

